#Django based Web application to support functionalities of Rice Mill industries.

Requirements:
=============
Open the command prompt in the current directory and execute the below commands:
   1. python2.7
   2. Django > 1.9

Dependencies:
=============

Setup:
======
   1. Install python2.7
   2. Open command prompt and navigate the python installed directory.
   3. Run python Tools\Scripts\win_add2path
   4. Run pip install --upgrade pip
   5. Run pip install virtualenv
   6. virtualenv <virtualenvname> #You virtual env name. Find more Info at: [https://virtualenv.pypa.io/en/stable/]
   7. cd <virtualenvname>
   8. Scripts\activate
   9. Copy project directory to the <virtualenvname> directory.
  10. Run pip install -U -r requirements.txt

Run:
====

Open the command prompt in the current directory and execute the below command.
   1. python manage.py runserver
